gomodel:SYNGO_1592  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig. 1 shows dendritic localisation in the vicinity of PSD-95-positive post-synapses. Fig. 3 (and 4) shows an increase of hnRNP A2/B1 in the vicinity of PSD-95 upon chemical stimulation of neuronal activity (primary hippocampal neurons, DIV 14-15). Experimental description: Wistar rats" ;
